#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.79"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.79:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.79:0.2"
msgid "8. Yamakavagga"
msgstr "8. Pairs"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 79. Parihānasutta → sekhaparihāniyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.79:0.3"
msgid "79. Parihānasutta"
msgstr "79. Decline"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.79:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "“These eight things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an8.79:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.79:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kammārāmatā, bhassārāmatā, niddārāmatā, saṅgaṇikārāmatā, indriyesu "
"aguttadvāratā, bhojane amattaññutā, saṃsaggārāmatā, papañcārāmatā—"
msgstr ""
"They relish work, talk, sleep, and company. They don’t guard the sense doors "
"and they eat too much. They relish closeness and proliferation."

msgctxt "an8.79:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "These eight things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.79:2.1"
msgid "Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "These eight things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an8.79:2.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.79:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na kammārāmatā, na bhassārāmatā, na niddārāmatā, na saṅgaṇikārāmatā, "
"indriyesu guttadvāratā, bhojane mattaññutā, asaṃsaggārāmatā, "
"nippapañcārāmatā—"
msgstr ""
"They don’t relish work, talk, and sleep. They guard the sense doors, and "
"they don’t eat too much. They don’t relish closeness and proliferation."

msgctxt "an8.79:2.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya "
"saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr "These eight things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.79:2.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
